data.description: Come see this gorgeous brick home! 3 bed 2 bath with glowing hard wood floors, and ceiling fans in most rooms. Featuring a welcoming front porch with a swing, a spacious living room and dinning room, 2 pantries, lots of closet space throughout the house, a new refrigerator and all appliances stay with the house. Come see the half of an acre beautiful fenced in back yard featuring a shed.
